description:
Zenitbet app for smartphones
Bookmaker Zenitbet has recently released a mobile app for iOS. You can download the app from App Store. What are the benefits of using the app to bet?
	•	Reduced data usage. Most importantly, web pages are loaded much quicker and you can view changes to the odds immediately when betting on live events.
	•	Betting on the go. You can make bets on sports when you are on public transport or even when walking. You can even bet on an event while watching it at the stadium.
	•	You will receive push notifications of upcoming events and event details.
	•	Optimized website navigation, including quick prematch/LIVE switch. 

The Zenitbet app offers:
	•	free access to Zenitbet. There is no need to look for working mirror websites. Authorisation is only required when you use the app for the first time;
	•	quick registration, like in the desktop version;
	•	easy navigation through the LIVE and Prematch sections, quick access to the required event; 
	•	live broadcasts in full-screen mode;
	•	fully-fledged personal account: betting history, e-Wallets;
	•	access to stats, results, live scores;
	•	deposits and withdrawals can be made using any popular payment system;
	•	Betgames, casino and slots.
The Zenitbet app for iOS has retained every feature of the desktop version. Its accessible design and full functionality make betting easier and quicker!
